verbose_text: HsSQM also catalyzed the mutarotation of various aldohexoses with an equatorial 2-hydroxy group, including d-galactose, d-glucose, d-glucose-6-phosphate (Glc-6-P), and d-glucuronic acid, but not d-mannose.
